# Code Review Rules

## Severity Tiers
- `[P0]` Security / data loss / broken functionality — block merge
- `[P1]` Logic errors / missing error handling — block merge
- `[P2]` Maintainability / test coverage — suggest fix
- `[P3]` Style / naming — optional

## Security (always check)
- No hardcoded secrets
- Parameterized queries only
- Input validated before use

## Comment Format
`[P1] Change X to Y — reason: Z`
